changelist.name: Default
changelist.comment: Removed "The old man the boat" test case. Cleaned up SceneModel, renamed it. Renamed SceneStatement to SceneCommand, cleaned up and refactored to adhere to command pattern.

Fixed some tests. Split EntityCreateRule into its' own file. Added Serializeable to Knowledge
Re-organised the project into modules, cleaned up the git repo.
Removed "old" files. (Should not have been comitted in the first place) Started work on the "ConcreteModelling" module.
Added the Renderer/Visualizer module. Refactorings and small changes.
